{"pid":"f1487620006fae48879a13f2c0836be50ef2efd6","tid":542093,"uid":2988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T23:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「事」急ar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽人係讀屎急"},{"pid":"f3f6d1bbe62d71a6c2471b238b07876a477557c2","tid":542093,"uid":51919,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T23:47:05.000Z","msg":"《三國志．魏書．李樂傳》記載了「事急馬行田」的故事。在魏文帝黃初六年，孫權率士五萬，親征北攻，直指江夏。文聘被困，大司馬曹真之侄厲涼受命返京。厲涼原計畫三天方可抵達京城。雖然當時規定，軍士若踩踏天地，依法須斬，但李樂仍建議「事急，馬行田，以短兩地之距，不者，石陽殆哉！」軍隊應穿過田地，以縮短距離。結果軍隊次日即到，大破孫權軍隊。"},{"pid":"7f55cb5062564c9493959ac7464fdf6628633ec6","tid":542093,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3f6d1bbe62d71a6c2471b238b07876a477557c2","tid":542093,"uid":51919,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T23:47:05.000Z","msg":"《三國志．魏書．李樂傳》記載了「事急馬行田」的故事。在魏文帝黃初六年，孫權率士五萬，親征北攻，直指江夏。文聘被困，大司馬曹真之侄厲涼受命返京。厲涼原計畫三天方可抵達京城。雖然當時規定，軍士若踩踏天地，依法須斬，但李樂仍建議「事急，馬行田，以短兩地之距，不者，石陽殆哉！」軍隊應穿過田地，以縮短距離。結果軍隊次日即到，大破孫權軍隊。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T00:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5999647e2bdfb3ad80353362da51eff762bb1c5","tid":542093,"uid":47496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1487620006fae48879a13f2c0836be50ef2efd6","tid":542093,"uid":2988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T23:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「事」急ar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽人係讀屎急"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T00:03:21.000Z","msg":"唔見肥絲大隻入嚟捉你地錯字<br />\n係喎呢d正字佢識條撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88e20c6c2859cf20ea86e842376863d5ad3e81d","tid":542093,"uid":30895,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d5999647e2bdfb3ad80353362da